Package org.gdal.ogr

Class FieldDefn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gdal.ogr.FieldDefn

  • public class FieldDefn
extends java.lang.Object
    Definition of an attribute of a FeatureDefn.

    The FieldDefn class is a binding for the C++ OGRFieldDefn class.
